decks.notes: This deck focuses on quickly utilizing creatures with infect to deal damage to the opponent. It utilizes cards like Phyrexian Crusader, Glistener Elf, and Plague Stinger to spread poison counters, while also using pump spells like Might of Old Krosa and Scale Up to increase their power. It includes protection spells like Vines of Vastwood and Blossoming Defense to keep the creatures alive, as well as disruption cards like Thoughtseize to control the opponent's hand. The goal is to overwhelm the opponent with infect damage before they can fully react.
